text: Alexandra "Alice" Teodorescu (born 2 May 1984) is a Swedish jurist with the FÃ¶retagarna organisation of Swedish entrepreneurs and a commentator on social and political issues. Teodorescu was born in Bucharest, Romania, but came to Sweden as a child in 1989 and was raised in Lund. She attended the Sture Academy, a training programme for young people owned and run by Timbro, a liberal think tank, and named after Sture Eskilsson. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1984 births Category:Swedish people Category:Jurists
